                        <interp inst="t18750920-name-47" type="given" value="EMILY"></interp>EMILY KILLDUFF</persName>
                  </hi>. I am barmaid at the Bird in Hand—on 3rd August, about 9.45 a.m., I served sharp with 1 1/2 <hi rend="italic">d</hi>. worth of gin—he gave me 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>.—I took it to my master, and then returned and told Sharpe that it was bad—he said "I beg your pardon, I am very sorry"—he gave me 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>.—I returned him the shilling and he left.</p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <persName id="t18750920-name-48" type="witnessName">
